data.description: Welcome home to this newly renovated home in Mountain Oaks in Stone Mountain. All new interior paint, new Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring, new carpet, new granite countertops, new stainless steel appliances, 2 new furnaces and new water heater. This home is in a cul de sac and has a nice private backyard. All bedrooms ($) are upstiars and 2 bathrooms are up, 1/2 on main. Kitchen, eating area and living room are all open and lead to the backyard. Dont miss this home!
